14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
16 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 180.14 of Title 17, unless there
17 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
18 The Oklahoma Corporation Commission is hereby required to
19 prepare and submit an annual report detailing all activities and
20 actions undertaken by any representative of the Commission in
21 dealings with the Southwest Power Pool. The report shall include,
22 but shall not be limited to:
23 1. A detailed account of all trips taken by Commission
24 representatives in connection with matters involving the Southwest
