4 representatives with the Southwest Power Pool or its
5 representatives, including dates, locations, and subject matters
6 discussed; and
7 3. A comprehensive summary of all votes taken by Commission
8 representatives on matters related to the Southwest Power Pool,
9 including the nature and outcomes of such votes.
10 The report shall cover all relevant activities undertaken during
11 the preceding calendar year and shall be completed and submitted no
12 later than January 31 of each year to the Speaker of the Oklahoma
13 House of Representatives and the President Pro Tempore of the
14 Oklahoma State Senate.
15 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
